createdata.import.gather.please select factors to make data table: making a table long, allows for easier manipulation of the data
createdata.import.gather.variable name: the new factor name of the gathered factors
createdata.import.gather.value name: the new factor name of the gathered values
createdata.import.gather.selection pattern: using regular expression select a list of factors to gather
createdata.import.gather.all: select all factors, factors may subsequently be deselected individually
